data.description: Absolutely Immaculate!  Located on a Cul-de-sac and Greenbelt with a beautiful creek just South of the home--an extremely rare find!   This is an open floor plan with a living room centered around a modern and elegant fireplace complimented by wood-look tile flooring and crown molding.  The kitchen has granite countertops, custom backsplash, a walk in pantry, all stainless appliances and a wrap around eat in bar perfect for entertaining.  The master suite is a perfect size with sloped 10ft ceilings; the bathroom has a double vanity, granite counter tops, tiled bath area, private toilet area and a separate shower, jetted tub, and a spacious walk-in closet with three-tiered clothing racks.  For outdoor living, enjoy the back porch with an extended patio, custom landscaping and an in ground sprinkler system as a bonus!
